<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.5.4">
<l>karumaṇi pūṇṭuveṇ ṇākaṇaintu kārimi lēṟṟaṇar tāḻntulāvum</l>
<l>orumaṇi yōcaiyeṉ ṉuḷḷantaḷ ḷavōrira vumuṟaṅ kātiruppēṉ</l>
<l>perumaṇi vāṉava ruccivaitta pēraru ḷāḷaṉpe  rumaipēci</l>
<l>kurumaṇi nīrkoḻik kumpuṟavil kuṟuṅkuṭik kēyeṉṉai yuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I am sleepless every night when the sound of the bell hanging,</l>
<l rend="indent">swaying from the neck</l>
<l>Of the dark, humped bull mating with a white cow wearing a dark bell,</l>
<l rend="indent">oppresses my heart.</l>
<l>[Ever] telling of the greatness of the lord of great graciousness</l>
<l rend="indent">who is kept on the heads of the celestials as a great jewel,</l>
<l>Make sure you take me to Kuṟuṅkuṭi where the waters cast up</l>
<l rend="indent">bright jewels in groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
